            <p>
              <strong>Challenge:</strong> This week, pick one of the
              four keys from Sūrat al-ʿAṣr that you feel you can focus
              on strengthening in your own life. Think of one online
              habit that drains time yet adds no good deed. Plan how
              to swap it for something that fits one of the four keys.
            </p>
            <span class="hashtag">#TrueSuccess</span>
            <span class="hashtag">#TimeManagement</span>
            <span class="hashtag">#FaithInAction</span>
          </div>
        </p>
